title: Bug 121170 - get column label from meta data object should return some user recognizable strings
OB: Calling IMetaData.getColumnLabel() before/after data extraction has different results.
EB: The method get column label from meta data object should return user recognizable strings. Before data extraction, the labels displayed to the end user should be the same as after extraction.
SR: To reproduce the issue, call the IMetaData.getColumnLabel() method before and after data extraction and compare the results.
